content.original: In an attempt to Improve the Combat Profile of LBX AutoCannons RISC Engineers created a completely new HE Shell. It causes massive explosion around the Impact. Upon receiving a Critical Hit, any remaining ammunition stored inside an Ammo Bin will explode dealing damage to the install location. Risk can be mitigated with the use of C.A.S.E.
